  <title>Gio.SimpleAction</title>
  <synopsis><code>
const Gio = imports.gi.Gio;

let simpleAction = new Gio.SimpleAction({
    <link xref='Gio.SimpleAction-name'>name</link>: value,
    <link xref='Gio.SimpleAction-parameter-type'>parameter_type</link>: value,
    <link xref='Gio.SimpleAction-state'>state</link>: value,
});
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>A <link xref="Gio.SimpleAction"/> is the obvious simple implementation of the <link xref="Gio.Action"/>
interface. This is the easiest way to create an action for purposes of
adding it to a <link xref="Gio.SimpleActionGroup"/>.</p>  <p>See also #GtkAction.</p>

